&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with inside sales and other local resources to analyze market potential and assist in developing strategies that drive market share growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a clear understanding of customer spend on &lt;strong&gt;equipment, parts, and services&lt;/strong&gt; related to installed base within the territory; document and communicate this information to location and headquarters management.&lt;/li&gt;
