&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership and relationship-building skills, detail-oriented, and action-driven.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in MS Excel, Word, and Outlook.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly motivated, self-starter with the ability to plan, organize, meet deadlines, and work independently in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physically able to climb structures, ladders, and scaffolds at job sites, inspect equipment, and safely work around crushers, screens, and conveyors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lift and/or move up to 75 pounds occasionally.&lt;/li&gt;
